$ON_WCATCSP
Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_WCATCSP(zc) From W1ENTSAL3
Onevent CONTROL Call C_WCATCSP(zc) From W1ENTSAL3
Onevent AFTER_CHANGE Gosub AMM_WCATCSP From W1ENTSAL3
Return

Subprog AS_WCATCSP(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(44777,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
## Action DEFHRCSP
Call DEFHRCSP(VALEUR,GCURLEG,GSOCIETE) From SUBHRCSP
If mkstat=2
 [M]WCATCSP(INDIC) = VALEUR
 Affzo WCATCSP(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_WCATCSP(zc) From W1ENTSAL3
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_WCATCSP(zc) From W1ENTSAL3
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_WCATCSP(zc) From W1ENTSAL3
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_WCATCSP(zc) From W1ENTSAL3
Gosub _AFF
End

Subprog C_WCATCSP(VALEUR)
